## Limitations

This report is based on available data and studies up to October 2023. The rapidly evolving nature of the pandemic means that new findings and insights may emerge, which could alter the current understanding of its impact on students. Additionally, the experiences of students can vary widely based on geographic, socioeconomic, and individual factors, which may not be fully captured in this report.